{"tid":1510383,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林大輝倡政府換人　稱鄭若驊李家超需負責","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:54.000Z","uid":268271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebde092cf7fb2cc2f4913614396918ea55e902c6","tid":1510383,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"全國政協委員林大輝日前獲特首林鄭月娥邀請，討論構建對話平台，他在電台節目形容政府「兩手空空」，在沒有創造有效條件下要求對話是不現實。他建議政府換人變陣，帶來新作風。<br />\n<br />\n 林大輝認為，要求示威行動平息後才對話，不現實不可行，政府需要展示出誠意才能創造對話空間。他指出，作為問責政府，反修例風波以來未能就社會形勢作出適當判斷的官員，有需要負上責任，其中律政司司長鄭若驊和保安局局長李家超責無旁貸。他覺得新人會帶來新希望，可能會為現時的困局帶來新方向。"},{"pid":"3466923a7bd10be77f50271d71fb3ab39d610255","tid":1510383,"uid":36651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8deb770b25a3db10be8f3b23442e10dffc129933","tid":1510383,"uid":70651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ac7fde612297bc6a45b28bd6c180a846f78568","tid":1510383,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=972b66e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=fe2b334e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/st